<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ك ف ى:</span> <span class="c2">(كَفَاهُ)</span> مَئُونَتَهُ يَكْفِيهِ <span class="c2">(كِفَايَةً)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(كَفَاهُ)</span> الشَّيْءَ. وَ <span class="c2">(اكْتَفَى)</span> بِهِ. وَ <span class="c2">(اسْتَكْفَيْتُهُ)</span> الشَّيْءَ <span class="c2">(فَكَفَانِيهِ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(كَافَاهُ)</span> <span class="c2">(مُكَافَاةً)</span> وَرَجَا <span class="c2">(مُكَافَاتَهُ)</span> أَيْ <span class="c2">(كِفَايَتَهُ)</span> . وَرَجُلٌ <span class="c2">(كَافٍ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(كَفِيٌّ)</span> مِثْلُ سَالِمٍ وَسَلِيمٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>